Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Sergeant James S. Hayes Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system constituting a portion of state route 14 as the "Sergeant James S. Hayes Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Sergeant James S. Hayes Memorial Highway"
